Usage: waldo.py [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
Options:
  -cal  --calibrate     reset and recalibrate buttons

  -h  --help            Args: None
                        Show this message and exit.

General:
  Connect raspberryPi with "keyboard" RYGBY before starting the raspberryPi; before running waldo.py.
  If you changed the length of the cable, run command "python waldo.py -cal". Restart raspberryPi or waldo.py.
  Buttons get their commands from the main config file (list "buttons").
